A CITY department store is celebrating after raising more than £3000 for BBC Children In Need. Store raises cash for kids A CITY department store is celebrating after raising more than £3000 for BBC Children In Need.Debenhams in Argyle Street took part in fundraising activities in a bid to support children around the UK.Store manager Craig Barker said: &quot;We are all really proud of the great achievement from the team.&quot; 